{
    "headline": "Hoppin\u2019 John",
    "name": "Hoppin\u2019 John",
    "description": "Hoppin' John is a hearty dish made by slowly simmering black-eyed peas with pork and vegetables, thought to bring luck and prosperity for the upcoming year. Our version has been simplified to use frozen black eyed peas.",
    "recipeCuisine": [
        "Southern"
    ],
